<br>
The best spot I have found is fighting Walrus men near the giant city. Search around until you find a Rhino, charm him, and then cast savge spirit on him. Then send him up against one of the walrus men or a blue walrus or whatever, and your rhino will slaughter them, hands down, you may need to toss the occasional dot on one if your pet is gettin low on health. The walrus men drop some very good sleeves for a druid, or so I hear as I have not gotten any yet, but I have gotten some neat armor and a no drop dagger from the Walrus, but the best part is the exp, these guys seem to be worth alot of exp.<br>
<br>
Hope this helps someone in search of a good spot since everything is perma farmed in Velious.<br>
